00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:04.040
So it was difficult.

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:06.786
And as you can see there,
that picture in the tent,

00:07:06.786 --> 00:07:07.910
this is one of the doctors.

00:07:07.910 --> 00:07:10.250
